# Netlify custom headers file.
# Everything in public/ is copied to the root of the build output (dist/).
# Netlify will read this file and apply the headers on deploy.
#
# These are the same headers requested for CORS + cross-origin isolation.
# See netlify.toml for a more maintainable version with comments.

# Apply to everything
/*
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
